      <div
        class="MuiBox-root css-1ldlsmb"
        id="faq-is-my-money-insured-sdic-coverage"
      >
        <h2
          class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h6 css-sylb4b-MuiTypography-root"
        >
          Is my money insured (SDIC coverage)?
        </h2>
        <p
          class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-15njp46-MuiTypography-root"
        >
          Yes. The Singapore Deposit Insurance Corporation (SDIC) insures up to S$100,000 per depositor per bank. This covers all SGD deposits in savings accounts, current accounts, and fixed deposits. If you hold more than S$100,000 in a single bank, the excess is not insured. Note: SDIC coverage does not apply to investment products, insurance policies, or foreign currency deposits.
        </p>
        <div
          class="MuiBox-root css-ah5j3r"
        >
          <span
            class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-caption css-1xtvbso-MuiTypography-root"
          >
            Sources
          </span>
          <ul
            class="MuiBox-root css-n1ol3p"
          >
            <li
              class="MuiBox-root css-1itv5e3"
            >
              <a
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-inherit MuiLink-root MuiLink-underlineAlways css-byaapg-MuiTypography-root-MuiLink-root"
                href="https://www.sdic.org.sg/di_scope_of_coverage/"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                target="_blank"
              >
                SDIC — Scope of DI Coverage
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium css-2e2mzl-MuiSvgIcon-root"
                  data-testid="OpenInNewIcon"
                  focusable="false"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M19 19H5V5h7V3H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-7h-2zM14 3v2h3.59l-9.83 9.83 1.41 1.41L19 6.41V10h2V3z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </a>
              <span
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-caption css-1f852r2-MuiTypography-root"
              >
                — SDIC covers SGD deposits in savings, current, and fixed deposit accounts. Does NOT cover foreign currency deposits, structured deposits, unit trusts, shares, or other securities.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li
              class="MuiBox-root css-1itv5e3"
            >
              <a
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-inherit MuiLink-root MuiLink-underlineAlways css-byaapg-MuiTypography-root-MuiLink-root"
                href="https://www.sdic.org.sg/di_faq/"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                target="_blank"
              >
                SDIC — Deposit Insurance FAQs
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium css-2e2mzl-MuiSvgIcon-root"
                  data-testid="OpenInNewIcon"
                  focusable="false"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M19 19H5V5h7V3H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-7h-2zM14 3v2h3.59l-9.83 9.83 1.41 1.41L19 6.41V10h2V3z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </a>
              <span
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-caption css-1f852r2-MuiTypography-root"
              >
                — Maximum coverage is S$100,000 in aggregate per depositor per DI Scheme member. CPFIS and CPFRS monies are aggregated and insured separately up to S$100,000.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li
              class="MuiBox-root css-1itv5e3"
            >
              <a
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-inherit MuiLink-root MuiLink-underlineAlways css-byaapg-MuiTypography-root-MuiLink-root"
                href="https://www.sc.com/sg/important-information/deposit-insurance-scheme-coverage-limit/"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                target="_blank"
              >
                Standard Chartered — SDIC Coverage Update
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  class="MuiSvgIcon-root MuiSvgIcon-fontSizeMedium css-2e2mzl-MuiSvgIcon-root"
                  data-testid="OpenInNewIcon"
                  focusable="false"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    d="M19 19H5V5h7V3H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-7h-2zM14 3v2h3.59l-9.83 9.83 1.41 1.41L19 6.41V10h2V3z"
                  />
                </svg>
              </a>
              <span
                class="MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-caption css-1f852r2-MuiTypography-root"
              >
                — Banks are required to disclose SDIC coverage limits to depositors. Coverage is per depositor per bank, not per account.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div
          class="MuiBox-root css-1uxf9r4"
